net.jokubasdargis.rxeither

Class Either<L,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.jokubasdargis.rxeither.Either<L,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    L - The type of left value.
    R - The type of right value.

    public abstract class Either<L,R>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a value of one of two possible types (a disjoint union.) Instances are either instance of Left or Right.
